<b>Kenapa awak memukulnya?
Dia pasti akan saman awak.</b>

978
01:10:05,460 --> 01:10:06,377
<b>Kenapa awak buat begitu?</b>

979
01:10:07,503 --> 01:10:09,547
<b>Awak pandai menyimpan
semuanya di dalam dan bertahan.</b>

980
01:10:15,220 --> 01:10:16,054
<b>Selamat tinggal.</b>

981
01:10:23,269 --> 01:10:24,187
<b>Gang-tae.</b>

982
01:10:28,483 --> 01:10:30,818
<b>Awak benar-benar pergi? Begitu sahaja?</b>

983
01:10:32,654 --> 01:10:34,072
<b>Tidak boleh ke awak minta maaf</b>

984
01:10:34,155 --> 01:10:35,782
<b>dan katakan ia adalah kesilapan?</b>

985
01:10:35,865 --> 01:10:36,866
<b>Ianya bukan...</b>

986
01:10:38,159 --> 01:10:38,993
<b>kesilapan.</b>

987
01:10:57,303 --> 01:10:58,137
<b>En Moon.</b>

988
01:10:59,264 --> 01:11:00,515
<b>Awak sangat bagus.</b>

989
01:11:00,598 --> 01:11:01,683
<b>Awak hebat!</b>

990
01:11:02,850 --> 01:11:05,019
<b>Oh tidak. Semuanya kerana lelaki itu.</b>

991
01:11:05,311 --> 01:11:07,855
<b>Gang-tae, kembali segera, okey?
Kami akan menunggu awak.</b>

992
01:11:14,070 --> 01:11:14,904
<b>En Moon...</b>

993
01:11:20,660 --> 01:11:21,744
<b>Kenapa dia tersenyum?</b>

994
01:11:22,412 --> 01:11:23,413
<b>Tidak, dia tidak.</b>

995
01:11:24,122 --> 01:11:25,957
<b>Dia digantung.
Dia mungkin hampir menangis.</b>

996
01:11:26,624 --> 01:11:29,836
<b>Tidak. Saya melihatnya tersenyum sebentar tadi.</b>

997
01:11:47,770 --> 01:11:49,772
<b>Apabila awak mahu melarikan diri,</b>

998
01:11:49,856 --> 01:11:51,941
<b>Beritahu saya. 
Dan saya akan berlari bersama awak.</b>

999
01:11:52,859 --> 01:11:55,069
<b>HOSPITAL PSIKIATRIK OK</b>

1000
01:12:57,256 --> 01:12:58,466
<b>Saya...</b>

1001
01:12:58,883 --> 01:12:59,884
<b>digantung.</b>

1002
01:13:02,595 --> 01:13:04,639
<b>Mereka tidak akan
bayar gaji saya semasa penggantungan saya</b>

1003
01:13:05,431 --> 01:13:07,183
<b>dan saya mungkin akan disaman.</b>

1004
01:13:09,519 --> 01:13:11,437
<b>Semuanya kacau bilau.</b>

1005
01:13:13,648 --> 01:13:14,899
<b>Awak kata sebelum ini</b>

1006
01:13:16,567 --> 01:13:18,027
<b>awak akan lari bersama saya</b>

1007
01:13:19,195 --> 01:13:20,154
<b>bila-bila masa saya mahu.</b>

1008
01:13:26,160 --> 01:13:27,078
<b>Saya mahu</b>

1009
01:13:27,954 --> 01:13:29,205
<b>berseronok dengan awak.</b>

1010
01:13:34,043 --> 01:13:34,919
<b>Sekarang.</b>

1011
01:13:41,134 --> 01:13:42,009
<b>Mari pergi.</b>

